%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Hung-tr%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-9l2KKaVBxta5Y-v_IMOuog">Hung trạch - 凶宅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/K%E1%BB%B7/poem-pDUW0PsGQfY5pvZk-0ynWw">Kỷ - 麂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/L%E1%BB%A5c-Ch%C3%A2u-tru%E1%BB%B5-l%C3%A2u/poem-5vF13G7-DM_9H7FxbIwGLQ">Lục Châu truỵ lâu - 綠珠墜樓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Kinh-Nam-thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-GrO2vAOFDwGICb-JExBRKA">Thu nhật Kinh Nam thuật hoài tam thập vận - 秋日荊南述懷三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
